From: L. David Baron <dbaron@dbaron.org>

Bug 916004 - Set the datasources attribute after the datasource has been synchronously loaded, to avoid intermittent failure caused by race condition.

Thanks to Neil Deakin for the suggestion.

MozReview-Commit-ID: BnX7vL109NF

